description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Atlanta, which features wig drama and a pizza party. On The Real Housewives of New Jersey, the women explore the Hamptons and argue about Jackie's money. Danny also discusses QIL Jessica Simpson's upcoming memoir and Brad/Jen.


RHOA: 7:56ish

RHONJ: 24:07
